m/images/DL_icon.svg\"></img></a></span></span></li><li id=\"ref-00008\" class=\"&#xA;                references__item&#xA;            \"><span class=\"references__note\">Ohkubo, M. &amp;amp;amp; Ishii, H. (1990) \"Design and Implementation of a Shared Workspace by Integrating Individual Workspaces\", <i>Proceedings of the Conference on Office Information System</i>, eds. Lochovsky, F. H. &amp;amp;amp; Allen, R. B., <i>SIGOIS Bulletin</i>, <b>11</b>(2, 3), pp. 142--146.  <span class=\"references__pub-id doi\"></span><span class=\"references__suffix\"><a class=\"google-scholar\" href=\"http://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&q=Ohkubo%2C+M.+%26amp%3Bamp%3B+Ishii%2C+H.+%281990%29+%22Design+and+Implementation+of+a+Shared+Workspace+by+Integrating+Individual+Workspaces%22%2C+Proceedings+of+the+Conference+on+Office+Information+System%2C+eds.+Lochovsky%2C+F.+H.+%26amp%3Bamp%3B+Allen%2C+R.+B.%2C+SIGOIS+Bulletin%2C+11%282%2C+3%29%2C+pp.+142%2D%2D146.+10.1145%2F91474.91502+\"target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"visibility-hidden\">Google Scholar</span><img src=\"/specs/products/acm/images/googleScholar.svg\" class=\"simple-tooltip__block--b\" alt=\"Google Scholar\"/></a></span><span class=\"references__suffix\"><a href=\"/doi/10.1145/91474.91502\" target=\"_blank\"><span class=\"visibility-hidden\">Digital Library</span><img class=\"simple-tooltip__block--b\" data-title=\"Digital Library\" alt=\"Digital Library\" src=\"/templates/jsp/_ux3/_acm/images/DL_icon.svg\"></img></a></span></span></li><li id=\"ref-00009\" class=\"&#xA;                references__item&#xA;            \"><span class=\"references__note\">Pollock, S. (1988) \"A Rule-Based Message Filtering System\", <i>ACM Transactions on Office Information Systems</i>, <b>6</b>(3), pp. 233--254.  <span class=\"references__pub-id doi\"></span><span class=\"references__suffix\"><a class=\"google-scholar\" href=\"http://scholar.google.com/scholar?hl=en&q=Pollock%2C+S.+%281988%29+%22A+Rule-Based+Message+Filtering+System%22%2C+ACM+